The '''dangleberry''' was a fruit that grew on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon of Endor]]. The orange-colored fruits, larger than other Endorian berries such as the [[Sunberry/Legends|sunberry]] or the [[rainbow berry]], grew individually on long vines from which they "dangled." The vines only bloomed once a year, and after they fruited, the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] would extract the [[Dangleberry juice|juice]] for consumption.<ref name="The Totem Master">"{{Ewoks|The Totem Master}}"</ref>

